rComments: One of the best profs I've ever had. Her lectures are awesome and she is so smart!
Very encouraging of discussion; finds value in everyone's input.

Professor Koshy was really nice and definitely cared about her students in class.  She picked some interesting texts about Asian American literature as well.  Papers were fairly graded and she put a lot of thought into her comments.
She is an amazing professor. I loved going to class every time. Her analysis of texts is brilliant and she is fascinating to listen too. Fabulous accent!
